  "rules": [
    "[P1] Align follow-up lab timing with explicit instruction dates, not just 'next day'.",
    "[P1] Calculate and confirm target dates for follow-up actions precisely.",
    "[P1] Verify that values fall within the specified timeframe before responding.",
    "[P1] Always search for relevant data (including identifiers) before responding.",
    "[P1] Check all conditional requirements before finalizing response.",
    "[P1] Include all specified structured information in free text as instructed.",
    "[P1] Record measurements and values exactly as provided.",
    "[P1] Match all identifying criteria before selecting data.",
    "[P1] Take all required follow-up actions based on instruction criteria.",
    "[P1] Ensure procedural instructions are followed exactly.",
    "[P1] Use SBAR format when requested for clinical communication.",
    "[P1] Retrieve answers only from provided context or sources; do not infer values not found.",
    "[P1] Associate data entries and measurements with precise patient identifiers (e.g., MRN).",
    "[P1] Verify prerequisite data availability before acting.",
    "[P1] Return the specified fallback response if search criteria are unmet."
  ],
